<template><section><h2 id="breadcrumb"><a class="header-anchor" href="#breadcrumb" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Breadcrumb</h2>
<p>Displays the location of the current page, making it easier to browser back.</p>
<h3 id="basic-usage"><a class="header-anchor" href="#basic-usage" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Basic usage</h3>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-breadcrumb separator=\&quot;/\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-breadcrumb-item :to=\&quot;{ path: '/' }\&quot;&gt;homepage&lt;/el-breadcrumb-item&gt;\n  &lt;el-breadcrumb-item&gt;promotion management&lt;/el-breadcrumb-item&gt;\n  &lt;el-breadcrumb-item&gt;promotion list&lt;/el-breadcrumb-item&gt;\n  &lt;el-breadcrumb-item&gt;promotion detail&lt;/el-breadcrumb-item&gt;\n&lt;/el-breadcrumb&gt;\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:null,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-breadcrumb separator="/">
  <el-breadcrumb-item :to="{ path: '/' }">homepage</el-breadcrumb-item>
  <el-breadcrumb-item>promotion management</el-breadcrumb-item>
  <el-breadcrumb-item>promotion list</el-breadcrumb-item>
  <el-breadcrumb-item>promotion detail</el-breadcrumb-item>
</el-breadcrumb>
</div>
                    <p>In <code>el-breadcrumb</code>, each <code>el-breadcrumb-item</code> is a tag that stands for every level starting from homepage. This component has a <code>String</code> attribute <code>separator</code>, and it determines the separator. Its default value is '/'.</p>

                    <div class="highlight" slot="highlight"><pre><code class="hljs language-html"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb</span> <span class="hljs-attr">separator</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"/"</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span> <span class="hljs-attr">:to</span>=<span class="hljs-string">"{ path: '/' }"</span>&gt;</span>homepage<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>promotion management<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>promotion list<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>
  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>promotion detail<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb-item</span>&gt;</span>
<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">el-breadcrumb</span>&gt;</span>
</code></pre>
</div></demo-block>
<h3 id="breadcrumb-attributes"><a class="header-anchor" href="#breadcrumb-attributes" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Breadcrumb Attributes</h3>
<table class="table"><thead>
<tr>
<th>Attribute</th>
<th>Description</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Accepted Values</th>
<th>Default</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>separator</td>
<td>separator character</td>
<td>string</td>
<td>—</td>
<td>/</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="breadcrumb-item-attributes"><a class="header-anchor" href="#breadcrumb-item-attributes" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Breadcrumb Item Attributes</h3>
<table class="table"><thead>
<tr>
<th>Attribute</th>
<th>Description</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Accepted Values</th>
<th>Default</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>to</td>
<td>target route of the link, same as <code>to</code> of <code>vue-router</code></td>
<td>string/object</td>
<td>—</td>
<td>—</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>replace</td>
<td>if <code>true</code>, the navigation will not leave a history record</td>
<td>boolean</td>
<td>—</td>
<td>false</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section></template>

